characters.name: Kael Ironheart
characters.lore: a battle-worn warrior, wields a blade forged in the heart of adversity, his eyes reflecting the shadows of countless victories and the weight of unspoken burdens.

characters.name: Sylara Blossom
characters.lore: A Wise Draenei Druid, Channels Nature's Harmony, Her Roots Intertwined With The Ages, Protecting Azeroth With The Tranquility Of Moonlit Groves.

characters.name: Elara Shimmer
characters.lore: a night elf mage, weaves arcane constellations, her timeless gaze holding the secrets of ancient spells, a guardian of arcane wisdom in moonlit realms.

characters.name: Brynn Stonecloak
characters.lore: a dwarf rogue, dances in the shadows, her nimble steps echoing ancient heists, a master of stealth with a heart veiled in gem-laden secrets.
